  "text": "Twisted equivariant K-theory for compact Lie groups is closely related to loop groups [CITATION_1] . It is natural to ask for a generalization of our construction of motivic twisted Ktheory to an equivariant setting involving group schemes. Problem 6.6: Develop a theory of motivic twisted equivariant K-theory.",
